SUMMARY:Linux Installfest
LOCATION:4820 Molson (métro Préfontaine)
DESCRIPTION:2026-05-29 16:00:00\n\n4820 Molson (métro Préfontaine)\n\nht
 tps://www.openstreetmap.org/node/2683768242\n\nSwitch to Linux with ease\n
 Whether you're a beginner or an experienced user\, this event will walk yo
 u through the process of installing Linux\, with the help of Insertech tec
 hnicians and volunteers.\nDiscover the benefits of a free\, secure\, and c
 ustomizable operating system\, while taking advantage of our support.\nIns
 talling Linux on your device lets you considerably extend it's lifespan.\n
 If your computer is slow and cluttered\, if it seems obsolete or if it isn
 't compatible with Windows 11... It still has a good life ahead of it ! A 
 slow and left for dead computer can still be used\, by installing another 
 operanting system\, safer and less computing power needed. Linux is a good
  example : it&nbsp\;is an open source software and it doesn't require givi
 ng up your personnal data to a giant tech company.\nMeet our experts and i
 nstall on your own machine a new tool\, rekindling your browsing and worki
 ng in complete safety\, and with the speed of the first days !\nResponsabi
 lity waiver\, terms and conditions:\nPlease make a backup of your files an
 d data.\nOnly one device per person.\nVolunteers are not professionnals. Y
 ou are responsible for your device.\nInstalling isn't always possible.\nPl
 ease bring your charger / power chord.\nFre event\, limited admission.\nFi
 rst come first served.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.openstreetmap.org/node/2683768242
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:resmtl-3
